description: The Sing Token Liquidity Pool NFTs offer a unique opportunity for those seeking to maximize their engagement with Sing Token. This limited edition NFT collection was distributed to those who acquired Sing Token during the special edition for liquidity addition. These NFTs can be staked to earn additional Sing Tokens, providing a means to actively contribute to the Sing Token ecosystem and receive rewards for your support.  #SingToken #MultiversX #NFT
